"content": "<h2>The urgency of the call to repent</h2>\n<h3>In the preaching of John the Baptist</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:2\">MAT 3:2</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:4\">MRK 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:3\">LUK 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>In the preaching of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:17\">MAT 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:3\">LUK 13:3</a></p>\n<h3>In the preaching of Peter</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:19\">ACT 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>In the preaching of Paul</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:21\">ACT 20:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:20\">ACT 26:20</a></p>\n<h2>The urgency of the need to proclaim the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:1-2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:1–4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:35-John4:37\">JHN 4:35–4:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:2\">2CO 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:2\">1TH 5:2</a> <em>in the light of the coming day of the Lord</em></p>\n<h2>Examples of urgent summons by officials</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:37\">NUM 22:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:8\">1SA 21:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:22\">DAN 3:22</a></p>",
